<h2 id="expressions">Expressions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>At once to insist upon having such a <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="report"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(流言蜚语)</code></b> universally contradicted.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Do your not know that such a report is <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="spread abroad"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(传得满城风雨)</code></b>?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Your coming to Loungbourn, to see me and my family will be rather a confirmation of it, if, indeed, such a report is <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="in existence"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(真实存在)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>I have not been in the habit of <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="brooking; not brook (on) sth - 不能容忍某事 (正式)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________([正式]容忍)</code></b> disappointment.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>My character has ever been <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="celebrated"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(以...获取别人的赞扬)</code></b> for its sincerity and frankness, and in a cause of such moment as this, I shall certainly not <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="depart from"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(背离)</code></b> it.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>It ought to be so; it much be so, while he retains <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="the use of his reason"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(保有理智)</code></b>. But your <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="arts and allurements"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(诡计和诱惑)</code></b> may, in a moment of infatuation, have made him forget what he owes to himself and to all his family. You may have <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="drawn him in"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(吸引他/勾引他)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>They are <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="descended on the maternal side"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(从母系方面传承)</code></b>, from the same noble line. And, on the father’s, from respectable, honorable, and ancient, though <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="untitled"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(未受封爵位的)</code></b> families.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
